'''Bangladesh Industrial Finance Company Limited''' (''BIFC'') is a [[joint venture]] [[Leasing]] and Financing Company. It is promoted by a group of foreign and local [[Sponsor (commercial)|sponsors]]. In August 1996, it was incorporated as a [[public limited company]] and in February 1998, it was licensed by [[Bangladesh Bank]] as a [[Non-bank financial institution|Non-Bank Financial Institution]]. <ref>http://www.linkedin.com/company/bangladesh-industrial-finance-company-limited</ref>
